{{version031}}
{{monster info}}

==Useful info==
'''Ironbound frosthearts''' are threatening ice mages guarding the [[Vaults]]. Like the player spell [[Frozen Ramparts]], Frosthearts can freeze the walls adjacent to the player to harm them. They inflict the [[Frozen]] status, slowing down player movement.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
These enemies are dangerous when faced in conjunction with other Vaults denizens, who will swarm you or pelt you with missiles if you leave a corridor or chokepoint to avoid Creeping Frost. Disable them with hexes or break LOS with them to buy some time to deal with other enemies first. 

==History==
{{CBA|0.32|ironbound frosthearts will have HD 11 instead of 12, to compensate a buff to the Frozen status.}}
*Prior to [[0.30]], Creeping Frost ignored cold resistance entirely.
*Ironbound frosthearts were added in [[0.27]].
